{"title":"割麦","authors":["雁伍"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":6,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"割麦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雁伍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵子南风吹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小麦遍地黄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老少齐下地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互助变工割麦忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刹刹刹小镰刀子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看着麦子笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺着垄眼向前扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三把两把打成捆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦个子排队满地躺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担子担、大车装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金黄黄的麦子走进了场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天里上地齐割麦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑夜里下地有武装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严防那坏分子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们查防要紧张。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦子不回家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天晚上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱到地里去查防。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}